definition: neck/collar/to lead/to receive/classifier for clothes, mats, screens etc
to (a place)/until (a time)/up to/to go/to arrive/(verb complement denoting completion or result of an action)

sentences.english: A: The boy will take your key and show you to your room.
sentences.chinese: 行李生将拿这钥匙把您领到房间去。

sentences.english: He was led to the exclusive counter by the staff of the shop.
sentences.chinese: 他被商店的职员领到了专门出售高档商品的柜台。

sentences.english: They led the father and son to Gessler, the cruel governor.
sentences.chinese: 他们把泰勒父子领到残暴的总督盖勒面前。

sentences.english: The detectives swore out a search warrant.
sentences.chinese: 侦探宣誓所控属实后领到一张搜查证。

sentences.english: She swore out a warrant for the arrest of the man who stole her car.
sentences.chinese: 她宣誓所控属实，因此领到了偷她车那个人的逮捕证。

sentences.english: He was at once conducted to the best room in the hotel, which Dolohov had taken for the occasion.
sentences.chinese: 他立刻被人领到多洛霍夫于是夜租用的上等客房里去。

sentences.english: Dormitory parents and cafeteria workers receive paychecks from the school.
sentences.chinese: 宿舍的舍长和自助食堂的工人从学校领到了工资。

sentences.english: He'll lovingly take you to your mansion in heaven.
sentences.chinese: 祂会慈祥地将你引领到天上的家。

sentences.english: When I arrive, I was taken to the warden.
sentences.chinese: 我到达时，被领到监狱长那里。

sentences.english: All the workers hired by the factory can get a year-end bonus.
sentences.chinese: 工厂里所有的在聘职工都可以领到年终奖金。

sentences.english: When Dr. Yoetz arrived, he was taken to Atzel's room.
sentences.chinese: 犹兹大夫来了以后被领到阿采尔的房间。

sentences.english: Police said an informant led narcotics officers to the house.
sentences.chinese: 警方说是一名告密者把缉毒警察引领到此的。

sentences.english: He finished regulation time with only four fouls.
sentences.chinese: 他在在这段调整时间内仅仅领到四次犯规。

sentences.english: Many needy students in the school have gotten student loan.
sentences.chinese: 大多数贫困生都领到了贷学金。

sentences.english: I got my clothing allowance of 100 yuan yesterday.
sentences.chinese: 我昨天领到了100元的服装费。

sentences.english: Love and knowledge, so far as they were possible, led upward toward the heavens.
sentences.chinese: 爱情与知识，总是可以把我引领到天堂的境界。

definition: neck/collar/to lead/to receive/classifier for clothes, mats, screens etc
to hand over to/to give to higher authority/to seek connections in high places
to take possession of/to get hold of
to transfer (income, profits etc) to higher authorities
